edc_admin <- dbGetQuery(framdw, "select vessel_name, vessel_id, limited_entry_permit_id LEP_ID, company_name, first_receiver_site_license, survey_year, review_status, missing_values, received_on, determined_on, survent_status, qaqc_status, address_line_1, address_line_2, city, state, zipcode, phone
           from edcsurvey_admin_v where survey_year > 2010") %>%
  merge(dbGetQuery(framdw, "select vessel_name, vessel_id, limited_entry_permit_id LEP_ID, company_name, first_receiver_site_license, survey_year, review_status, missing_values, received_on, determined_on, survent_status, qaqc_status, address_line_1, address_line_2, city, state, zipcode, phone 
                  from fram_analysis_current.edcsurvey_admin_v 
                   where  edcsurvey_dbid not in (select distinct edcsurvey_dbid from fram_analysis_current.edcsurvey_edcdata_v where edcsurvey_dbid is not null)"), all = T) %>%
  mutate(DUE_DATE = ymd(paste0((SURVEY_YEAR+1), '-09-01'))) %>%
  mutate(LATE = ifelse(RECEIVED_ON > DUE_DATE+10, 'LATE',ifelse(RECEIVED_ON < DUE_DATE+10 | RECEIVED_ON == DUE_DATE+10, 'ON TIME', NA)))
